波折，而且注意20歲之前容易出現災難的事情發生。</blockquote><br />\n追問 幾時會有女朋友？幾時發達？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b24c017f9f394ac24546a87e7e8250650106a3d","tid":398794,"uid":126681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T00:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/085648_6b18665161561f292c0fd9e5152f1c8e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F085648_6b18665161561f292c0fd9e5152f1c8e.jpg&h=a489986c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/085650_6c78bfe58f47a441683527822dcae9ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F085650_6c78bfe58f47a441683527822dcae9ab.jpg&h=0caedc7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n21歲 男 事業 學業"},{"pid":"827970b3fb98b6ab921036b588bec10df62d8462","tid":398794,"uid":57065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:22:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/15/102125_4bf91e20fdb97fc7973e17fde3ad9827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F15%2F102125_4bf91e20fdb97fc7973e17fde3ad9827.jpg&h=c6a0bb2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1991年 男<br />\nThx"},{"pid":"d3994fb13a32f8e7052a290b9c5a6e34744edd10","tid":398794,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T02:49:13.000Z","msg":"死去支那啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"7a7ebe011f4e49211bfbca62ec8a549a043a49c8","tid":398794,"uid":146619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:38:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/104057_da4557b69750cb2eb69dc1260786a6a2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F104057_da4557b69750cb2eb69dc1260786a6a2.jpg&h=e1c6ecbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n92男</blockquote><br />\n生命線彎曲，而且短，你要注意健康問題，特別是28歲到35歲之間病痛問題多，反覆，這兩年注意有外傷出現，感情方面看17歲18歲有桃花但是23到25歲感情不順利，自己注意，婚姻中年出現問題，出現大島紋。"},{"pid":"9762e29b04f20f8189b737d98d2416e5336cce49","tid":398794,"uid":146619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/103039_a9f29e2335441cb8a9bd48ea694b2dfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F103039_a9f29e2335441cb8a9bd48ea694b2dfd.jpg&h=c8be695a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1993 男</blockquote><br />\n你屬於假斷掌，今年是24歲，猶豫不決，想法多不夠積極主動，缺少點膽量魄力，感情方面22到24歲不順，注意腸胃，23到24歲發生一件事情十分壓抑，注意休息，生命線短，前列腺，腎方面，體質目前弱，上火"},{"pid":"0373652dc108a99e73f28cb97ba69ae53a4a0fcc","tid":398794,"uid":146619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:41:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/103654_aeb6903af156261dc55dfab44219ec24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F103654_aeb6903af156261dc55dfab44219ec24.jpg&h=e0b48b10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n23男<br />\n唔該大師</blockquote><br />\n  你的手相看紋路挺多，在你13歲14歲就出現好感的人，桃花異性，但是之後沒有聯繫，15到16歲感情心煩的事情多，而且出現壓抑的事情，17歲18歲也是看到桃花，感情方面今年是23歲，也有異性，但是你的感情不好，32歲之前順利，就算結婚也出現問題。事業線被很多橫紋沖段，你破財地方多，注意存錢。"},{"pid":"af20daca45b9dcc728ff5a3974f4b69c2730799f","tid":398794,"uid":146619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1994 23歲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/14/104126_079e5ba2027ca53a78a26dc62f31b1e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F14%2F104126_079e5ba2027ca53a78a26dc62f31b1e2.jpg&h=9d2be9e5&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n感情方面19歲20歲有桃花，但是21歲到23歲波折，25到27歲也是波折，都是分手歲數，感情是28歲29歲後才看到希望，今年情況不好，注意腸胃，壓抑，精神不好，事業方面不錯有貴人，中年起運。"}]}